@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="container" style="padding: 20px;">
    <h2>About Propane Driver</h2>
    <h3>The delivery driver utility app designed specifically for drivers.</h3>

    <div style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px;">
        <p>
            PropaneDriver was created for Class A and B propane delivery drivers. The delivery apps
            provided by most companies are not driver-centric — they're designed for dispatchers and
            back-office staff, not for the person behind the wheel.
        </p>
        <p>
            This app puts the driver first: streamlined route views, quick delivery logging,
            and the features that make a long day on the road less stressful and less error-prone.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
